<p>英 /'sɪmələ(r)/    美 /'sɪmələr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>相似的；类似的</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some body language is similar everywhere.
有些肢体语言在各个地方都相似。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) similar to:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mencius was a thinker whose teachings were very similar to those of Confucius. 
孟子是位思想家，他的学说与孔子的非常相似。</p><footer>外研③ – 5</footer></div>

